{"tid":1592533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如何令多啲和理非參加9.28, 9.29, 10.1 集會遊行","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T06:31:24.000Z","uid":291321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b17a4b405db1fda13bf5598247388e96b88770c","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:03:05.000Z","msg":"最好用宗教集會名義， 上次8.31都好成功， 和理非最緊要搵個合法理由"},{"pid":"547459f8234a34d440b8a86969469d0ad749c65f","tid":1592533,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"5a0ce6d12455fb79abf46af883929d6902e6d105","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:03:41.000Z","msg":"11111"},{"pid":"35207db3138f248728061b09d47cc808cd70c6e3","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:03:51.000Z","msg":"22222"},{"pid":"b1954f8b05623ce62617688cb901d2982c65d1f3","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:04:01.000Z","msg":"33333"},{"pid":"e8f5bc8d20c00dda03827e475b33c4276b04251a","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"44444"},{"pid":"5c9fbc4f7b5f2f0886e1dcb40a7b7f49c093932a","tid":1592533,"uid":72775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:04:17.000Z","msg":"集思廣益"},{"pid":"04418716ee9b0368a6a5e15bf5712bf7931ffab9","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"55555"},{"pid":"17bff13a030a0aac91c2865c4147ce242d1ff3e0","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:04:33.000Z","msg":"66666"},{"pid":"ed34d12b4d910f313389fa4674a2dddafdd06e57","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"77777"},{"pid":"093e4d30e00b5f24e4d7ffa8424233735e22662e","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:04:57.000Z","msg":"88888"},{"pid":"2d4294e37b7c40adb41657b6e1e6ccdd931b4b00","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"99999"},{"pid":"0cea1bf5752c4779740b00192dd2f9f50ac6c684","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:05:28.000Z","msg":"100000"},{"pid":"e0d562554d2363e0e5637a2bc7adabc4de7a9aea","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:05:38.000Z","msg":"110000"},{"pid":"95df39469b92e11b18e36de4df9e155f86e937b9","tid":1592533,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"宣傳<br />\n<br />\n《行動》928 雨傘5週年 集會 yellow object<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590313</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa2692030177f6bd6fd9d42d0bb330b1f90d86ff","tid":1592533,"uid":291321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"最好用宗教集會名義， 上次8.31都好成功， 和理非最緊要搵個合法理由"},{"pid":"c857b1fd113dbaf173bfe5b4930f8613f2aa4976","tid":1592533,"uid":278786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T20:50:55.000Z","msg":"可以考慮對於不反對通知書有plan A plan B.<br />\n另外，如何做到有一百萬人以上，對和理非而言，最重要是不用申請不反對通知書而且有合法途徑。否則乜文宣都無用。<br />\n有條橋，就是抄何妖，佢話921清潔香港不用申請不反對通知書，仲串到撤銷遊行申請。<br />\n咁佢無被人拉無人告，心理上就可以宣傳：我地9.29/10.1搞的都是清潔香港行動，沿香港島電車路主線，人人執垃圾。口號可以加「清除香港垃圾，路線只有一條」，大家brainstorm 一下。<br />\n<br />\n人流控制方面：<br />\n可以呼籲港島人在自己區清潔；<br />\n九龍東人在鰂魚涌的香港殯儀館（象徵送中）以東，新界東人在鰂魚涌以西;<br />\n九龍西人在中環遮打花園以西，新界西人在中環以東。中環同殯儀館兩個地點也較方便過海人士。<br />\n<br />\n另一個重點，係需要有號召力的人或機構呼籲，大肆宣傳，俾和理非感覺既合法又多人陪，咁就安心參加。<br />\n<br />\n宣傳時戴埋頭盔，講明無集會丶無遊行路線，各人自發清除垃圾，自行發揮。<br />\n<br />\n利申：和理非"},{"pid":"212ef0edfe4acff8155b93a2462c15b75a4285e6","tid":1592533,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"今晚 1900-2100 添馬公園"}]}